---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home">
  <section class="hero-box">
    <div class="hero-overlay">
      <div class="cta-container">
        <p class="cta-label">Workshop // Available Pieces</p>
        <a href="https://www.etsy.com/shop/fouza" target="_blank" class="hero-cta-button">
          Visit the Etsy Shop
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-meta">Ref. 2025 // Collection Archive</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="story-container">
      
      <div class="story-header">
        <span class="blueprint-id">Ref. No. 1974-JVS</span>
        <h2 class="story-title">From Architecture to the Forge</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="story-body">
        <p>
          For the beginning of my adult life I was determined and excited to become an architect and interior designer. While going to college and pursuing this goal, I began taking silver smithing classes as a part of my art requirement.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          I finished college and started my designing career but discovered I was spending a lot of time making things for myself and gifts for others. After quite a few years of trying to live two lives, I determined that the small intricate fascinating world of silver and gold smithing was my stronger passion.
        </p>

        <p>
          I began training in earnest both with professional schooling and master goldsmiths. I've been doing it now for over 20 years and I still love it. There are always new challenges to tackle, wonderful people to meet, problems to solve, and itsy bitsy details to work out.
        </p>

        <p class="cta-text">
          If you have any questions from what you see here, or if you'd like to order something special for yourself or a loved one, please feel free to <a href="/contact">contact me</a>. I also have an <a href="https://www.etsy.com/shop/fouza" target="_blank">Etsy Store</a>, where you can find many things to tickle your fancy.
          Thanks for taking the time to read my story! If you're dying for more, check out my <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank">Instagram account</a>.
        </p>

        <div class="signature-block">
          <p>Keep on smiling,</p>
          <p class="name">Jen Van Schmus</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mechanical-footer">
        <div class="gear-dot"></div>
        <div class="long-line"></div>
        <div class="gear-dot"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero-box {
    width: 100%;
    height: 800px;
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    background-image: url('/site-assets/hero-main.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  /* NEW HERO CTA STYLING */
  .cta-container {
    text-align: center;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .cta-label {
    font-family: 'Special Elite', monospace !important;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    color: #888;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .hero-cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 15px 40px;
    border: 1px solid #000;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1);
  }

  .hero-cta-button:hover {
    background: #000;
    color: #fff;
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .hero-meta {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 40px;
    right: 40px;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    color: #aaa;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* RE-ALIGNED STORY STYLES */
  .story-section { padding: 120px 0; background: #fff; display: flex; justify-content: center; }
  .story-container { max-width: 700px; width: 100%; padding: 0 40px; }
  .story-header { text-align: left; margin-bottom: 60px; border-left: 1px solid #eee; padding-left: 30px; }
  .blueprint-id { display: block; font-size: 10px; color: #ccc; letter-spacing: 0.3em; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .story-title { font-size: 2.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; line-height: 1.1; }
  .story-body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 30px; text-align: justify; }
  .story-body p { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #444; }
  
  .cta-text { 
    margin-top: 20px; 
    padding: 40px; 
    background: #fcfcfc; 
    border-left: 2px solid #eee;
    font-size: 1rem !important;
  }
  
  .cta-text a { font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 4px; }

  .signature-block { margin-top: 40px; text-align: left; }
  .signature-block .name { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-top: 5px; color: #111; }

  .mechanical-footer { margin-top: 100px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; opacity: 0.3; }
  .long-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: #eee; }
  .gear-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border: 1px solid #000; border-radius: 50%; position: relative; }
</style>
